ur_rna.RNAstructureUI.utilities

Class FileFilters

  • java.lang.Object
    • ur_rna.RNAstructureUI.utilities.FileFilters

  • public class FileFilters
extends java.lang.Object
    A list of constants for common file extensions. Note that most file-specs end with a bar character. This is meant to allow easy concatenation of filters.
